      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.w-layout-grid > div.stats26_content-right > p.text-size-medium",
      "en": "IOI Oleochemical maintains rigorous certification standards across its global footprint. Every facility meets or exceeds industry requirements for responsible sourcing, occupational safety and supply chain integrity. These certifications provide independent verification of our commitment to sustainable practices.",
      "cn": "IOI Oleochemical 在全球各地坚守严格的认证标准。每座生产基地均达到或超越行业对负责任采购、职业安全与供应链完整性的要求。这些认证为我们对可持续实践的承诺提供独立验证。"
