      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.w-layout-grid > div.layout220_item > p",
      "en": "Our supply chain excludes operations on peatland or areas of high conservation value",
      "cn": "我们的供应链不涉及泥炭地或高保护价值区域的运营"
    },
    {
