      "context": "div#w-node-_0a67f569-b321-004f-3b43-eac7548857b7-8392438b > div.margin-bottom > h2.heading-style-h2",
      "en": "Every shipment tracked from source to delivery",
      "cn": "每一批货物均从源头追踪至交付"
    },
    {
      "id": "t62",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div#w-node-_0a67f569-b321-004f-3b43-eac7548857b7-8392438b > div.margin-bottom > p.text-size-medium",
      "en": "We document certified palm oil through our supply chain with precision. Our commitment to transparency lets stakeholders verify product origin and handling at each stage.",
      "cn": "我们以严谨的方式记录经认证棕榈油在供应链中的全程流转。透明度承诺让各利益相关方可在每个环节核实产品来源与处理过程。"
