      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.w-layout-grid > div.layout90_content-right > p.text-size-medium",
      "en": "We listen to concerns from workers, suppliers, communities and stakeholders. IOI Oleochemical maintains open channels for reporting issues related to labour practices, environmental impact or ethical conduct. Every report receives fair review and timely response, ensuring accountability throughout our supply chain.",
      "cn": "我们倾听来自员工、供应商、社区与各利益相关方的关切。IOI Oleochemical 设有畅通的申诉渠道，受理涉及劳动实践、环境影响或道德行为的问题反映。每一项反映都将获得公正审议与及时回应，以确保全供应链的责任承担。"
    },
